{
  "stem": "22840.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Hlinka Guard was very eager to-- to be [? as ?] perceived as strong as SA or the SS.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It just followed the same patterns, nothing innovative, nothing new.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Concentration camp, deportations, the Slovaks were paid for everybody who was deported.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were willing participants in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jews had to wear yellow stars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a small yellow star, because I was a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents had a bigger yellow star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a whole set of books on-- on his deeds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think we can-- we can summarize it here, for two reasons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A, it's lengthy, and B, I avoided reading those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Suffice it to say, that in the Jewish Museum, in Bratislava, now on the Slovak non-Communist government, there's a large display of his work with his name and-- and portrait and pictures.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was awarded a-- he was awarded various honors by the Slovak pre-Communist government and by Jewish organizations.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a large forest, of well above 1,000 trees, planted in his name, in Israel, by the survivors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His name is in the Jewish encyclopedia, not a big article, but an article mentioning him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I said, it's very, very well-documented in-- in his memoirs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS] One thing he did, he stayed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had the opportunity to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He-- he had a certificate to go to then Palestine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He could have been alive today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in the end of the '30s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was part of the Zionist movement, very unusual for rabbis at the time, to be part of the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although, the Neologs were better in that sense.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
